# Model dropdown labels. MUST be string IDs (Kodi parses literal
# label="3.1 Flash Lite" as integer 3 -> built-in string "Videos").
# MUST also be in the 30000-32999 addon range -- anything 33000+ is
# reserved for Kodi built-ins, so Kodi ignores our po entry and
# falls back to the built-in lookup (same Videos/Music bug). The
# first attempt at this fix used 33010-33013 and reproduced the bug
# exactly. Moved into the gap inside the Translation category.
