msgstr "Optional. If you have DarkSubs installed, you do not need Wyzie at all -- clicking any non-Hebrew subtitle in DarkSubs will trigger AI translation automatically. Wyzie is only useful if you have NO other subtitle addon and want a one-click online source from inside this addon. 1000 requests/day on the free tier at store.wyzie.io/redeem."

